  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Humble\" title=\"House Humble\"><img alt=\"None.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/5/58/None.svg/50px-None.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/5/58/None.svg/75px-None.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/5/58/None.svg/100px-None.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\">Burton Humble</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Humble\" title=\"House Humble\"><img alt=\"None.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/5/58/None.svg/50px-None.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/5/58/None.svg/75px-None.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/5/58/None.svg/100px-None.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiance</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_Humble\" title=\"House Humble\">House Humble</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Ironborn\" title=\"Ironborn\">ironborn</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i> (appears)</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Burton Humble</b> is an <a href=\"/index.php/Ironborn\" title=\"Ironborn\">ironborn</a> raider in <a href=\"/index.php/Victarion_Greyjoy\" title=\"Victarion Greyjoy\">Victarion Greyjoy</a>'s crew aboard the <i><a href=\"/index.php/Iron_Victory\" title=\"Iron Victory\">Iron Victory</a></i>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Burton_Humble&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Dance_with_Dragons\"><i>A Dance with Dragons</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Burton_Humble&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Dance with Dragons\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>Burton accompanies <a href=\"/index.php/Victarion_Greyjoy\" title=\"Victarion Greyjoy\">Victarion Greyjoy</a> when the <a href=\"/index.php/Iron_Fleet\" title=\"Iron Fleet\">Iron Fleet</a> sails to <a href=\"/index.php/Slaver%27s_Bay\" title=\"Slaver&#39;s Bay\">Slaver's Bay</a>. When the fleet sails past the <a href=\"/index.php/Stepstones\" title=\"Stepstones\">Stepstones</a>, Burton knocks out four of Maester <a href=\"/index.php/Kerwin\" title=\"Kerwin\">Kerwin</a>'s teeth for smiling at him. When <a href=\"/index.php/Moqorro\" title=\"Moqorro\">Moqorro</a> is brought aboard the <i><a href=\"/index.php/Iron_Victory\" title=\"Iron Victory\">Iron Victory</a></i>, Burton suggests sacrificing the <a href=\"/index.php/Red_priest\" title=\"Red priest\">red priest</a> to the <a href=\"/index.php/Drowned_God\" title=\"Drowned God\">Drowned God</a> before he can call a curse down on them.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd56.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd56.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Burton_Humble&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Radwd56.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd56.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_56\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Chapter 56\">Chapter 56</a>, The Iron Suitor.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403121457\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.076 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.302 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 437/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 10394/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 4432/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 204/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 8/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 531/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.210/7.000 seconds\nLua virtual size: 6.45 MB/50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%  293.385      1 -total\n 97.77%  286.828      1 Template:Infobox_character\n 97.01%  284.601      1 Template:Infobox\n 10.03%   29.423     12 Template:Infobox_value\n  3.35%    9.828      3 Template:Infobox_label\n  1.71%    5.009      1 Template:Ref\n  1.13%    3.304      1 Template:Ref/core\n  0.47%    1.383      1 Template:References\n  0.34%    0.989      1 Template:Main_other\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in